  "annotations": [
    {
      "id": "an_0a13adce",
      "reference_id": "d580024f-f391-49e3-b50e-212c7b33c520",
      "text": "The authors look to explore how SRL can lead to performance by having 140 online students and 466 b-learning students fill the MSLQ. The results show that B-Learning students engage more in help-seeking and peer-learning, while online students engage more in SRL behavior on the remaining constructs. ",
      "provenance": {
        "page_id": "d580024f-f391-49e3-b50e-212c7b33c520"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "an_a6efba1b",
      "reference_id": "d580024f-f391-49e3-b50e-212c7b33c520",
      "text": "Moreover, the authors found that, whether online or in B-Learning, there were no significant differences when it comes to the predictive power of different SRL constructs. ",
      "provenance": {
        "page_id": "d580024f-f391-49e3-b50e-212c7b33c520"
      }
    }
  ],
